(54, 2, 'WGS606', NULL, NULL, 'StarbucksÃÂ® Sampler', 'Warm conversation and enjoying small moments of peace during a hectic day - this is what the StarbucksÃÂ® coffee and biscotti gift box is meant for.  Slow down for a cup of soul-soothiing Breakfast blend, a House Blend, Caffe VeronaÃÂ® or Sumatra and a sweet bite of biscotti. A perfect gift for that favorite teacher or colleague - they will appreciate your thoughtfulness. ', 'cat', 39.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS606_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS606_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(55, 2, 'WGS607', NULL, NULL, 'TazoÃÂ® Tea Temptations', 'Sip your way to a beautiful day with this comforting gift. Stocked with an assortment of the finest Tazo teas from Zen and Passion to Organic Chai and Earl Grey, they are ready to be enjoyed in an earthenware ceramic mug. Topped off with the sweetness of a Theo organic chocolate bar and 2 biscotti cookies, this gift is presented in a simple but elegant gift box.', 'cat', 39.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS607_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS607_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(56, 2, 'WGS608', NULL, NULL, 'StarbucksÃÂ® Tea and Coffee Box', 'This is a gift meant to be shared and enjoyed. An assortment of TazoÃÂ® Teas, and two blends of StarbucksÃÂ® finest - Breakfast Blend and Caffe VeronaÃÂ®, 2 signature mugs and 2 biscotti, packaged in a beautiful gift box and topped with a raffia ribbon. ', 'cat', 49.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS608_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS608_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(57, 2, 'WGS626', NULL, NULL, 'Starbucks Gratitude Basket', 'An extra special way to say "Thank You", our StarbucksÃÂ® Gratitude Basket will send the message you are trying to express. Fresh, juicy oranges and crisp green and red apples start them off, as well as three different bags of delicious StarbucksÃÂ® Coffees - Breakfast Blend, Caffe Verona and House Blend. Add an assortment of tempting TazoÃÂ® Teas and Nonni''s biscotti for a great "Thank You" gift to give - and receive! ', 'cat', 59.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS626_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS626_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(58, 2, 'WGS629', NULL, NULL, 'StarbucksÃÂ® Celebration', 'Celebrate life''s special moments with a gift everyone is sure to love - StarbucksÃÂ®! This bountiful basket holds everything your special recipient needs for their mornings. Take a break and share a cup of StarbucksÃÂ® Breakfast Blend, House Blend, Costa Rica or Caffe Verona coffee. Sip a steaming cup of TazoÃÂ® Calm and Zen Tea from one of the two ceramic StarbucksÃÂ® mugs, or enjoy the delicious rich taste of Starbucks ViaÃÂ® Ready Brew or Classic Hot Cocoa. Recharge and re-energize with Nonni''s biscotti and Walkers shortbread cookies for a completely satisfying mid-morning or afternoon moment. ', 'cat', 109.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS629_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS629_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(59, 2, 'WGS635', NULL, NULL, 'StarbucksÃÂ® Evergreen Coffee and Tea', 'Send thanks and good wishes with this gift of StarbucksÃÂ® Coffee and TazoÃÂ® Tea delights! A perfect way to show your gratitude or send your appreciation for a job well done, this lovely cream basket contains three classic StarbucksÃÂ® coffees: French Roast, Caffe Verona and Starbucks VIAÃÂ® ready brew, six TazoÃÂ® Tea bags and two sweet Nonni''s biscotti, as well as a classic green StarbucksÃÂ® logo mug. Exquisite and ready to be enjoyed! ', 'cat', 49.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS635_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS635_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(60, 2, 'WGS653', NULL, NULL, 'StarbucksÃÂ® Get Up & Go Box', 'This gift will be a hit for the StarbucksÃÂ® coffee lover on the go. The hot/cold travel mug is sure to become a daily favorite and it comes with four types of StarbucksÃÂ® coffee including Pikes Place Roast, Cafe Estima, Blond roast and Sumatra Blend. For StarbucksÃÂ® anytime, they will also enjoy the VIA ready brew in Italian Dark roast flavor and spiced chocolate and cherry walnut biscotti.', 'cat', 59.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS653_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS653_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(61, 2, 'WGS654', NULL, NULL, 'Classic StarbucksÃÂ® Coffee & Cocoa', 'You can''t go wrong with a classic gift of perfect StarbucksÃÂ® proportions! A natural Kraft box adorned with the Starbucks logo holds two Starbucks ceramic mugs and Starbucks Breakfast Blend, House Blend and Sumatra coffees. This gift also includes hot cocoa, Walker''s shortbread medallions and shortbread fingers, gingerbread biscotti and caramel wafer. Classically Starbucks! ', 'cat', 49.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS654_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS654_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(62, 2, 'WGS655', NULL, NULL, 'StarbucksÃÂ® Coffee, Cocoa & Chocolate to Share', 'Satisfy those caffeine cravings with a gift of true StarbucksÃÂ® variety! There''s something for everyone included in this naturally delicious selection. Three blends of StarbucksÃÂ® coffee are featured: House Blend, Breakfast Blend and French Roast. A box of salted caramel hot chocolate will satisfy that sweet craving and Via ready-brew caramel flavored coffee is perfect for travel or on-the-go quick fixes. Also included are two ceramic StarbucksÃÂ® logo mugs, spiced chocolate biscotti and a TCHO organic chocolate bar. All presented in a natural kraft box and tied with an elegant green ribbon. ', 'cat', 99.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGS655_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGS655_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:53:15'),
(63, 2, 'WGD401', NULL, NULL, 'Eli''s Sampler Cheesecake', ' The best of Eli''s all in one cheesecake. Eli''s Sampler Cheesecake has a blend of 4 mouthwatering flavors. 8" cheesecake has three slices each of the following flavors: Original Plain - all natural rich and creamy cheesecake; Apple Streusel cheesecake - made with fresh apple slices, cinnamon and crunchy streusel; Turtle cheesecake - caramel cheesecake with a layer of caramel topped with crunchy toasted pecans and chocolate drizzle; and White Chocolate Raspberry cheesecake - topped with a mirror of raspberry puree and splashes of white chocolate backed on a chocolate cookie crust. 8" dia. Cheesecake comes pre-cut and ships frozen. Serves 12 and weighs approximately 2 lbs.', 'ecc', 39.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGD401_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGD401_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:54:35'),
(64, 2, 'WGD405', NULL, NULL, 'Eli''s Cheesecake Co. Turtle Cheesecake', ' The Eli''s Cheesecake Co. Turtle Cheesecake turns any get-together into a sweet celebration! This turtle temptation, from one of the world''s best cheesecake companies, Eli''s Cheesecake Company of Chicago, is a creamy caramel cheesecake topped with a layer of caramel, bittersweet chocolate drizzle and a sprinkle of pecan pieces to create the ultimate indulgence. This cheesecake is 8" in diameter, ships frozen and has 14 pre-cut slices. ', 'ecc', 39.99, 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/WGD405_d1.jpg', 'http://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/WGD405_t1.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-09 07:54:35'),
