(144, 1, 'C3-4793', NULL, NULL, 'The Sunny Sentiments Bouquet', 'The Sunny Sentiments Bouquet is a blooming expression of charming cheer. Brilliant yellow roses and Peruvian Lilies are paired with white traditional daisies and green button poms to create a memorable bouquet. Accented with lush greens and arranged in a classic clear glass vase, this bouquet is a wonderful way to celebrate any of life''s special moments.', 'v', 49.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/C3-4793.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/C3-4793_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheap-flowers-tomorrow.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(145, 1, 'T235-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Gracious Lavender Basket', 'Soothing lavender, respectful purple and compassionate pinks are combined beautifully in this basket overflowing with pretty flowers, sincerity and sympathy. A lovely way to share your thoughts and pay tribute to someone special. A profusion of purple, pink and lavender blooms such as roses, carnations, larkspur, matsumoto and monte cassino asters and much more are delivered in a round wicker basket.', 'fb', 124.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T235-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T235-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/funeral-gift-baskets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(146, 1, 'S53-4570', NULL, NULL, 'Solace Ivy Planter', 'The Solace Ivy Planter is an exquisite way to convey your wishes for peace and comfort in the face of the grief your special recipient feels for the loss of their loved one. A 6-inch variegated ivy plant displays its lush, vibrant foliage seated in an oval whitewash woodchip basket accented with a pale yellow ribbon, to create a gift of warmth and soft serenity they will cherish.', 'p', 49.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S53-4570.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S53-4570_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/gift-plants.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(147, 1, 'T38-1A', NULL, NULL, 'She''s Lovely', 'Thank heaven for little girls! And for adorable arrangements like this one! Perfect for new moms, new babies and girly-girls of all ages, this sweet basket of pink petals is sure to get a warm welcome! Pretty pink hydrangea, roses and spray roses along with Queen Anne''s lace are delivered in a charming white basket that''s all wrapped up with a pink bow. Say hello to beauty, cutie!', 'c', 74.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T38-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T38-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/floral-centerpieces.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(148, 1, 'fam114', NULL, NULL, 'Long Stem Red Roses Boxed', 'One dozen boxed long stem red roses and greens.', 'r', 64.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/fam114.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/fam114_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/valentine-flower.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(149, 1, 'C3-4431', NULL, NULL, 'The Daylight Bouquet', 'The Daylight Bouquet bursts with sun-filled excitement and cheer expressed through each radiant bloom. Gorgeous yellow roses and gerbera daisies are accented with the golden hues of Viking chrysanthemums and solidago arranged with lush greens in a clear glass square tapered vase to create a splendid way to brighten their day.', 'v', 54.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/C3-4431.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/C3-4431_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flowers-next-day.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(150, 1, 'S14-4467', NULL, NULL, 'Treasured Memories Standing Spray', 'The Treasured Memories Standing Spray is a rich and colorful way to express your unending love and devotion to the departed. An exceptional arrangement of red roses, burgundy carnations, burgundy mini carnations, red gerbera daisies and white button poms are accented with a variety of lush greens. A red ribbon with the word, "Beloved," embossed in a gold metallic lettering, finishes this beautiful display for their final farewell service. Displayed on a wire easel.', 'fs', 174.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S14-4467.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S14-4467_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-spray.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(151, 1, 'T34-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Once Upon a Daisy', 'This bright and sunny bouquet is as sweet as a fairy tale ending. Perfect for baby showers, birthdays and beyond. Beautiful light blue hydrangea, cheerful yellow gerberas and white daisy spray chrysanthemums are delivered in a light blue Satin Cylinder that comes complete with a pretty light blue ribbon. Blue skies ahead!', 'c', 69.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T34-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T34-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/party-centerpieces.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(152, 1, 'T96-2A', NULL, NULL, 'Secret Garden Basket', 'It will be no secret how you feel about the person lucky enough to receive this beautiful basket. Whether it''s someone you work with or someone you live with. Someone near or someone far. This gift is overflowing with robust beauty and lively energy. A pink kalanchoe, hypoestes, green nephthytis and both Boston and maidenhair ferns are delivered in a delightful round wicker basket. Variety of plants and container style may vary.', 'p', 74.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T96-2A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T96-2A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/deliver-rare-plants.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(153, 1, 'fam801', NULL, NULL, 'One Dozen Red Roses and Large Teddy Bear', 'Twelve of the highest quality red roses professionally arranged with greens and babies breath and accompanied with a large cuddly teddy bear. Color and style of bear may vary.', 'r', 109.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/fam801.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/fam801_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/valentine-gift-baskets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(154, 1, 'C19-4849', NULL, NULL, 'The Beautiful Expressions Bouquet', 'The Beautiful Expressions Bouquet, blooming with tulips, roses and calla lilies, is an exquisite flower bouquet set to impress. Pale pink tulips, lavender roses, white open-cut calla lilies, peach hypericum berries and lush greens are beautifully arranged in a violet flared glass vase to create a wonderful way to convey your sweetest emotions on your anniversary, for their birthday or just to brighten their day.', 'v', 115.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/C19-4849.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/C19-4849_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flowers-for-birthday.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(155, 1, 'S34-4515', NULL, NULL, 'Truly Loved Basket', 'The Truly Loved Basket exudes fantastic color, warmth and cheer to convey your most heartfelt sympathies for their loss. Purple tulips, fuchsia spray roses, lavender carnations, lavender larkspur, lavender button poms, jade spider chrysanthemums, green hypericum berries and lush greens are beautifully arranged in a brown willow basket to create a wonderful way to show how much you care.', 'fa', 89.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S34-4515.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S34-4515_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/exotic-flower-delivery.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:05'),
(156, 1, 'T27-2A', NULL, NULL, 'Basket Full of Wishes', 'Wishes do come true, by the basketful, actually. This delightful arrangement is so full of sunny blossoms, it even includes a pretty yellow butterfly who obviously feels right at home, basking in the warmth. Brilliant yellow spray roses, asiatic lilies, miniature gerberas, carnations, alstroemeria, button spray chrysanthemums and delightful greenery are joined by a delicate butterfly in an oval basket. It''s a basket of wonder and wishes!', 'c', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T27-2A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T27-2A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/table-decoration-ideas.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(157, 1, 'fam101', NULL, NULL, 'One Dozen Red Roses Arranged', 'Twelve highest quality long stem red roses professionally arranged with greens in a clear vase.', 'r', 69.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/fam101.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/fam101_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/30th-anniversary-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(158, 1, 'C19-4846', NULL, NULL, 'Splendid Day Bouquet', 'The Splendid Day Bouquet, set with roses and asters, creates the perfect bouquet for any of life''s special moments. Lavender roses, lavender monte casino asters, purple matsumoto asters, green hypericum berries, green button poms and lush greens create a stunning flower bouquet perfectly arranged in a clear glass bubble bowl vase to create a wonderful thank you, happy birthday or congratulations gift.', 'v', 62.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/C19-4846.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/C19-4846_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/birthday-delivery-ideas.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(159, 1, 'S17-4472', NULL, NULL, 'Forever in Our Hearts Casket Adornment', 'The Forever in Our Hearts Casket Adornment is a beautiful accent piece that adds that extra touch of elegance to their final farewell service. Red roses and mini carnations are eye-catching and bright arranged amongst white hydrangea, larkspur, snapdragons and Queen Anne''s Lace. Tied together with a white grosgrain ribbon, this gorgeous bouquet is a lovely way to say goodbye to your beloved.', 'fl', 64.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S17-4472.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S17-4472_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/inside-casket-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(160, 1, 'T27-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Oh Happy Day by Teleflora', 'Oh, what a happy day it will be for whoever is lucky enough to have this vase full of joyful and jubilant blossoms delivered to them. Perfect for Happy Birthday or Happy Any Day, this pretty arrangement is sure to inspire smiles! Dazzling green roses, carnations and button spray chrysanthemums, yellow asiatic lilies and gladioli along with fresh greens fill a rectangular glass vase. Come on! Say it and send it like you mean it? Oh Happy Day!', 'c', 54.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T27-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T27-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/simple-centerpieces.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(161, 1, 'fam802', NULL, NULL, 'One Dozen Red Roses and Small Teddy Bear', 'Twelve of the highest quality red roses professionally arranged with greens and babies breath and accompanied with a small cuddly teddy bear. Color and style of bear may vary.', 'r', 99.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/fam802.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/fam802_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/valentine-delivery-gifts.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(162, 1, 'S6-4447', NULL, NULL, 'Exquisite Tribute Standing Spray', 'The Exquisite Tribute Standing Spray is an elegant display of sweet serenity. White roses, Asiatic lilies, chrysanthemums and mini carnations are artfully arranged amongst emerald palm fronds and lush greens. Accented by white satin ribbon and standing on a wire easel, this standing spray is an outstanding way to honor the life of your loved one.', 'fs', 149.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S6-4447.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S6-4447_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/spray-of-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06'),
(163, 1, 'C18-4858', NULL, NULL, 'The Beloved Bouquet', 'The BelovedÂ® Bouquet brings roses and carnations together in a sophisticated arrangement to offer your love and affection. Lavender roses, green carnations, purple stock, green hypericum berries, green button poms and lush greens are gorgeously arranged in a clear glass cubed vase lined with variegated ti leaves for a modern and stylish effect, making this a wonderfully romantic gift of sweetness set to brighten their day.', 'v', 74.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/C18-4858.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/C18-4858_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-next-day-delivery.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:06');
