(183, 1, 'B4-4112', NULL, NULL, 'The Bright Autumn Centerpiece', 'The Bright Autumn Centerpiece spins the magic of the Fall season with each sun-kissed petal to set your gathering space aglow with blooming beauty.  Two taper candles are surrounded by a gorgeous arrangement consisting of orange Asiatic Lilies, gerbera daisies, and roses with golden Peruvian Lilies, burgundy cushion poms and assorted greens to create the perfect addition to your Autumn celebration.', 'c', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/B4-4112.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/B4-4112_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/2nd-anniversary-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:07'),
