(288, 1, 'T09J400A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Stratford Gardens', 'For a gift that?s reminiscent of a stroll through the English countryside, send this stunning mix of pink and peach roses mingled with cool lavender chrysanthemums, arranged in a misty lavender vase. It?s as charming as a cottage garden. Pink spray roses, waxflower and hot pink miniature carnations, plus peach roses and lavender cushion spray chrysanthemums ? accented with bupleurum, seeded eucalyptus and oregonia ? are delivered in a lavender sweetheart vase. Style and color of vase may vary.', 'v', 49.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T09J400A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T09J400A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/bouquet.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(289, 1, 'T8-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Always a Lady', 'A romantic gift like this one is always appreciated. An eye-catching display of roses and lilies is perfectly arranged in a feminine vase which makes a beautiful and lasting impression. Elegant white roses and sweet pink asiatic lilies are hand-arranged with greens. It''s the perfect way to show you love her always and forever.', 'v', 79.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T8-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T8-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/bouquet-of-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(290, 1, 'S28-4501', NULL, NULL, 'Eternal Rest Standing Heart', 'The Eternal Rest Standing Heart bursts with love and sweet comfort to honor the deceased at their final farewell service. Lavender roses, pink carnations, purple button poms, lavender chrysanthemums, pink gladiolus and pink hydrangea are beautifully arranged in a the shape of a heart and displayed on a wire easel to create a stunning display of warm affection that will last in the hearts of friends and family for years to come.', 'fh', 249.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S28-4501.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S28-4501_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/my-heartfelt-sympathies.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(291, 1, 'T6-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Cupid''s Creation by Teleflora', 'Classic beauty and romance to spare, thanks to the graceful lines of a Couture Vase filled with stunning roses ? the iconic flower of love. Like the arrow released from Cupid''s bow, this gorgeous bouquet will go straight to your lover''s heart. Exquisite red and pink roses, white and light pink spray roses and greens are perfectly arranged in a lovely vase. This is an inspired way to celebrate your love.\nVase may vary.', 'v', 94.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T6-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T6-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-bouquets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(292, 1, 'T5-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Lavish Love', 'Lovely reds and pinks come together in this lavishly romantic anniversary gift. Sweetly sentimental, this combination of colors and flowers is a delightfully fresh way to say "I love you." Radiant red roses and spray roses along with pretty in pink asiatic lilies are beautifully arranged in a stylish glass vase. It''s a beautiful way to celebrate a romance that deepens with each passing year.', 'v', 84.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T5-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T5-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-bouquet.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(293, 1, 'S46-4550', NULL, NULL, 'Sweet Peace Bouquet', 'The Sweet Peace Bouquet is an elegant way to convey your deepest sympathies for the loss of their child. White roses, daisies, and Oriental lilies are sweetly accented with light blue delphinium, lush greens and a light blue organza ribbon, arranged to perfection in a clear glass vase, to create an exquisite way to offer comfort during this time of grief and sadness.', 'fa', 74.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S46-4550.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S46-4550_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/S46-4550.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(294, 1, 'T4-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Make Me Blush', 'It''s fun to be flirty! Send a dozen roses to the one you love and she just might make you blush. Especially if the dozen roses in question are this gorgeous! This arrangement is sweet and innocent as can be. Of course, it''s a bit sassy and a whole lot sexy, as well. Sending a dozen perfectly pink roses and white limonium arranged in a glass vase to the woman you love shows that you know how much fun love is! And every woman appreciates that!', 'r', 79.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T4-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T4-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-for-valentine.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(295, 1, 'S12-4465', NULL, NULL, 'Dearly Departed Casket Spray', 'The Dearly Departed Casket Spray bursts with the love and passion that the deceased had for their life and loved ones. Rich red roses and carnations are gorgeously arranged amongst lush greens and accented with a red satin ribbon to create the ideal adornment for their casket at their final farewell service.', 'fc', 274.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S12-4465.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S12-4465_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/casket-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(296, 1, 'T157-3A', NULL, NULL, 'Sunny Siesta', 'Know someone who could use a little pick-me-up? Sending this pretty summer arrangement will definitely do the trick. Light orange roses and alstroemeria, yellow asiatic lilies and orange gerberas are delivered in an organza ribbon-wrapped cylinder vase. Siesta or fiesta ? it''s all good.', 'v', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T157-3A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T157-3A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/bouquet-of-roses.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(297, 1, 'S25-4491', NULL, NULL, 'Wishes & Blessings Bouquet', 'The Wishes & Blessings Bouquet is a stunning way to offer your condolences for their loss and commemorate the life of the deceased. Soft pink roses, spray roses, Oriental lilies, hydrangea and larkspur are brought together in a clear glass vase to create an eye-catching display of soft serenity.', 'fa', 79.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S25-4491.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S25-4491_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/sympathy-flower-online.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(298, 1, 'T24-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Fly Away Birthday Bouquet', 'Make birthday spirits soar by sending this fabulously fun birthday bouquet and balloon. Bright primary colors make it perfect for guys and gals. Years may fly by but that doesn''t mean birthday celebrations need to! Brilliant orange roses, yellow alstroemeria, red carnations and miniature carnations, yellow daisy spray chrysanthemums, purple statice and a big bright balloon are all delivered in a beautiful cobalt blue vase. It''s a thumbs-way-up choice in birthday gifts! Vase may vary.', 'v', 69.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T24-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T24-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheapest-birthday-gift.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(299, 1, 'T21-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Dazzling Day Bouquet', 'Dazzle someone on their special day with a balloon-festooned bouquet. Delightful blossoms and a shiny birthday balloon are sure to make their day! Pink roses, yellow gerberas and daisy spray chrysanthemums, dark pink alstroemeria, light yellow carnations, light pink matsumoto asters and miniature carnations are a mere sampling of what''s included in this dazzling gift. When you add the stylish vase and super happy balloon, this gift will surely rise above all expectations!', 'v', 79.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T21-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T21-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/birthday-gift-baskets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(300, 1, 'S46-4549', NULL, NULL, 'Tender Treasure Casket Spray', 'The Tender Treasure Casket Spray is a beautiful way to honor the life of the child taken too soon. White roses, daisies, monte casino asters, Asiatic lilies, and mini carnations are accented with light blue delphinium and a light blue organza ribbon to be displayed on top of the casket at their final farewell service.', 'fc', 219.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S46-4549.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S46-4549_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/casket-sprays.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(301, 1, 'T18-2A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Pink Pink Bouquet', 'Think pink. Think pretty. Think present. This beautifully feminine bouquet makes a wonderful gift for any woman. Light pink asiatic lilies and alstroemeria share the spotlight with pink roses and waxflower. Lovely lavender stock and seeded eucalyptus have been added to complete this bouquet that''s delivered in a pink Jewel Vase. A perfectly pink present!', 'v', 79.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T18-2A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T18-2A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/bouquet-delivery.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(302, 1, 'S44-4542', NULL, NULL, 'Graceful Tribute Wreath', 'The Graceful Tribute Wreath creates a stunning presentation of love''s serenity for their final farewell service. Red roses, carnations and gerbera daisies are accented with burgundy mini carnations and a variety of lush greens to create a sweeping arrangement that glides across the face of a snow white wreath consisting of chrysanthemums making this a remembrance for one who has touched your life like none other. Displayed on a wire easel.', 'fw', 239.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S44-4542.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S44-4542_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-wreaths.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(303, 1, 'T18-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Simply Sweet', 'Sometimes life''s simplest pleasures deliver life''s most poignant feelings. Take this sweet bouquet. Soft colors, beautiful flowers in a yellow vase that''s wrapped in a pretty pink satin bow. Simple? You bet. Special? For sure! Bright yellow roses, pink asiatic lilies and alstroemeria, light yellow miniature carnations, lavender daisy spray chrysanthemums and pink limonium are gorgeously arranged in a pretty yellow vase, complete with a satin bow. Sweeter than sweet!\nVase may vary.', 'v', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T18-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T18-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/birthday-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(304, 1, 'S45-4543', NULL, NULL, 'Salute to a Patriot Standing Heart', 'The Salute to a Patriot Standing Heart is the perfect tribute to a fallen marine. A pearly white heart consisting of chrysanthemums is accented with an arrangement of red roses, white Asiatic lilies and lush greens, as well as, a white banner that reads, "Semper Fidelis USMC," to create an incredible presentation at their final memorial service. Displayed on a wire easel.', 'fh', 199.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S45-4543.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S45-4543_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/S45-4543.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(305, 1, 'T17-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Perfectly Pleasing Pinks', 'A perfectly pleasing mix of sweet springtime blossoms make this a truly happy gift. So full of feminine flowers and fun feelings, this is the perfect arrangement to make her smile. Dazzling white spray roses, hot pink gerberas and matsumoto asters, pink carnations, lavender cushion mums, light pink stock and much more fill a lavender vase. Vase may vary.', 'v', 94.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T17-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T17-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/beautiful-flower-bouquets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(306, 1, 'T14-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Joyful Jubilee', 'Sending a jubilation of flowers is a joyful way to brighten any celebration. This particular arrangement is eye-catching, colorful and captivating. Hot pink spray roses and gerberas, dark pink Sweet William, lavender matsumoto and purple monte cassino asters are joined by greens in an exclusive lavender keepsake vase. Tied with a ribbon, it''s ready to shine. Vase may vary.', 'v', 64.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T14-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T14-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheap-bouquets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(307, 1, 'S15-4470', NULL, NULL, 'Soul''s Splendor Arrangement', 'The Soul''s Splendor Arrangement is a rich display of the love shared throughout the life of the deceased. Brilliant red roses are elegantly displayed in a white designer plastic urn and accented with lush greens and red satin ribbon to create a beautiful tribute to honor your special relationship.', 'fb', 199.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S15-4470.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S15-4470_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/funeral-gift.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(308, 1, 'F1-315', NULL, NULL, 'Mixed Spray', 'A tribute spray of pink carnations, yellow spray mums, lilies, and gypsophila. Appropriate for funeral home.', 'fs', 124.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/F1-315.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/F1-315_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-wreaths-for-doors.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(309, 1, 'T11-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Wondrous Wishes by Teleflora', 'Awe and wonder. That''s what''s included in this magical bouquet. It''s a beautiful mix of radiant blossoms in a stunning glass vase. Brilliant blue hydrangea, orange roses, light pink asiatic lilies, hot pink gerberas, pink alstroemeria, purple chrysanthemums and more fill a fabulously feminine vase. Send wonder with your lovely wishes! Vase may vary.', 'v', 79.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T11-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T11-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-bouquet-delivery.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `type_id`, `product_no`, `page_id`, `supplier_id`, `name`, `description`, `category`, `price`, `image`, `thumb_image`, `flowerwyz_image`, `status`, `ord`, `created`) VALUES
(310, 1, 'T42-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Sunny Smiles', 'What better gift to send someone than a sunny smile? Think how much that sentiment delivered in the form of this beautiful and cheerful bouquet will mean to whoever''s on your mind today. Dazzling green roses, peach spray roses, yellow asiatic lilies, alstroemeria and solidago along with beautiful leafy greens are delivered in a yellow Serendipity vase. Send a sunny smile today! \nVase may vary.', 'v', 49.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T42-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T42-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheap-flower-bouquets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(311, 1, 'S7-4449', NULL, NULL, 'Sweet Solace Bouquet', 'The Sweet Solace Bouquet is a divinely elegant arrangement that encourages peace and offers your sympathy. Brilliant white roses and calla lilies are simply set amongst lush greens in a clear glass gathering vase to create a meaningful gift that will help your special recipient through this trying time of grief and loss.', 'fa', 99.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S7-4449.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S7-4449_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/condolences-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(312, 1, 'T41-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Garden Parade', 'You''ll want to put this colorful bouquet on your hit parade of gifts to send. Bold primary colors and a perfect mix of flowers make it great for men and women of all ages. In other words, it''s a perfect arrangement. Yellow roses, alstroemeria, and button spray chrysanthemums, red miniature gerberas and matsumoto asters along with purple statice, salal and fern are delivered in a lovely hurricane vase. It''s a garden parade to be proud of!', 'v', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T41-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T41-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/a-bouquet-of-roses.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:13'),
(313, 1, 'T37-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Cotton Candy', 'What a sweet way to celebrate the arrival of sugar and spice and everything nice! This pretty arrangement will delight any new mom or mom-to-be, that''s for sure! Feminine flowers fill a charming ribbon-wrapped vase. It''s a beautiful thing! Pretty pink roses, spray roses and miniature carnations, white button spray chrysanthemums, lavender limonium and green pittosporum fill a spring glass vase that''s wrapped with a pink satin ribbon. It''s confection perfection!', 'v', 69.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T37-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T37-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-bouquets-delivered.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(314, 1, 'T29-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Here''s to You by Teleflora', 'Whether you are raising a vase to celebrate a birthday, a new job or any other occasion, here''s the one to send. So bright, so beautiful, so colorful ? men and women alike will appreciate your thoughtfulness. Brilliant blue hydrangea, yellow roses, red gerberas and miniature carnations, yellow button spray chrysanthemums are delivered in a vase. Here''s to celebrating!\nStyle of vase may vary.', 'v', 69.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T29-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T29-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheap-wedding-bouquets.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(315, 1, 'S46-4547', NULL, NULL, 'Precious Child Standing Heart', 'The Precious Child Standing Heart is a beautiful way to commemorate a life lost too soon. White chrysanthemums and white button poms form a gorgeous white heart-shaped wreath lined around the outside with a bright blue ribbon. Accented with an ivory plush bear at the center and a white banner that reads, "Precious Child," in gold metallic lettering, this sweet presentation is a lovely addition to their final farewell service. Displayed on a wire easel.', 'fh', 239.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S46-4547.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S46-4547_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/S46-4547.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(316, 1, 'T46-1A', NULL, NULL, 'How Sweet It Is', 'How sweet it will be when this dazzling arrangement arrives at someone''s door. Very vibrant. Very vivacious. And very, very pretty. Light orange roses, orange spray roses, hot pink carnations and matsumoto asters, red miniature carnations and more are delivered in a lovely glass vase. Be sweet and send this one today!', 'v', 49.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T46-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T46-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-arrangements-weddings.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(317, 1, 'S16-4471', NULL, NULL, 'Sincerity Casket Spray', 'The Sincerity Casket Spray is a wondrous presentation of fresh color and beauty. Rich red roses and carnations are eye-catching and elegant in an arrangement of white hydrangea, larkspur, snapdragons, Queen Anne''s Lace and assorted lush greens to create a lovely display meant to bedeck the top of their casket, bringing comfort and peace to those grieving the loss of the departed.', 'fc', 299.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S16-4471.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S16-4471_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheap-casket-sprays.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(318, 1, 'T32-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Amazing Daisy', 'Celebrate the brightest of occasions with this cheerful bouquet of happy-faced daisies presented in a graceful, vase. Yellow roses and spray roses, white daisy spray chrysanthemums, solidago and pittosporum fill a lovely Inspiration vase. Amazingly pretty!', 'v', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T32-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T32-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/cheap-mothers-day-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(319, 1, 'S21-4484', NULL, NULL, 'Loving Remembrance Wreath', 'The Loving Remembrance Wreath is a blushing display of grace and beauty to honor the life of the deceased at their final tribute. Pink roses, Oriental lilies, gladiolus, hydrangea and carnations are brought together with lush greens to form the shape of a wreath, offering warmth and comfort with its sweetly sophisticated elegance. Displayed on a wire easel.', 'fw', 279.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S21-4484.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S21-4484_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/funeral-wreath.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(320, 1, 'T58-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Meet Me in Provence by Teleflora', 'With a beauty reminiscent of the south of France, this proud and pretty arrangement holds nothing back. The colors, the flowers and the feeling of Provence are all present and accounted for in this wonderful bouquet. Yellow roses, spray roses and asiatic lilies, white spray roses and stock and the ever-delightful light blue delphinium are delivered in a vase. C''est magnifique\nStyle of vase may vary.', 'v', 74.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T58-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T58-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/romantic-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(321, 1, 'S3-4442', NULL, NULL, 'Treasured Tribute Wreath', 'The Treasured Tribute Wreath offers peaceful wishes of heartfelt sympathy with each delicate bloom. Bright white roses, Asiatic lilies, mini carnations and cushion poms are beautifully arranged to form an elegant accented with lush and vibrant greens. Displayed on a wire easel, this gorgeous tribute is a wonderful symbol of eternal life and sweet serenity. Approximately 22 inches in diameter.', 'fw', 224.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S3-4442.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S3-4442_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flower-wreath.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(322, 1, 'T55-1A', NULL, NULL, 'Teleflora''s Heavenly & Harmony', 'Heavenly hues and pretty petals are in perfect harmony in this gorgeous arrangement. Lovely for a birthday, anniversary or just because, it''s simply stunning! Light pink roses, white asiatic lilies, Queen Anne''s lace and salal are beautifully arranged in a glass vase. Heaven sent? Well, someone will think you''re an angel for sending it!\nStyle of vase may vary.', 'v', 69.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T55-1A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T55-1A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/order-flowers.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(323, 1, 'S47-4556', NULL, NULL, 'Angel''s Cross Easel', 'The Angel''s Cross Easel is a graceful tribute to honor the life and faith of the deceased. Pink mini carnations and baby''s breath are lovingly arranged in the shape of a cross, accented with a pink satin ribbon around the outside and displayed on a wire easel, to create a wonderful way to express your love for the departed.', 'fx', 199.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/S47-4556.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/S47-4556_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/S47-4556.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
(324, 1, 'T55-2A', NULL, NULL, 'Arrive In Style', 'This beautiful bouquet will most certainly arrive in style! Ready for the runway, as it were. A delightful combination of light colors and lovely flowers, it''s simply beautiful. Light pink roses, white asiatic lilies, alstroemeria, cushion spray chrysanthemums and statice are delivered in a stylish vase. Style to spare!', 'v', 59.95, 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/products/T55-2A.jpg', 'https://www.floristone.com/flowers/thumbnails/T55-2A_t.jpg', 'https://www.flowerwyz.com/images/flowers-shop.jpg', 'Y', 0, '2016-03-02 11:49:14'),
